eagleBom.Description: Open Source Hardware Logo This logo indicates the piece of hardware it is found on incorporates a OSHW license and/or adheres to the definition of open source hardware found here: http://freedomdefined.org/OSHW
EZ is for Kits. There is no tStop (covering up the top side of the pads with mask). This helps the beginner see which side they should be soldering too.
